    <item>
      <title>行业陷入危机 中国叫停新建钢厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/china-puts-brake-on-new-steel-capacity-with-industry-in-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为应对需求大幅下滑导致行业利润下滑、出口激增的情况，中国政府突然暂停了新钢铁厂的审批。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/china-puts-brake-on-new-steel-capacity-with-industry-in-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 01:53:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万科将展示房地产危机对中国银行造成多大影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/vanke-to-show-extent-of-property-crisis-that-s-bruising-chinese-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万科企业股份有限公司和中国海外发展有限公司在公布业绩时应会继续对中国房地产行业描绘悲观的前景，显示出政府刺激措施的局限性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/vanke-to-show-extent-of-property-crisis-that-s-bruising-chinese-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 01:47:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场动荡之际，印度的“最佳投资点”吸引债券基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/india-s-sweet-spot-lures-bond-funds-amid-global-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球基金已连续 14 周向印度债券市场投入资金，这是今年第二次连续购买，证明了印度在全球金融市场动荡中仍具有吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/india-s-sweet-spot-lures-bond-funds-amid-global-market-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚政府向反对派提出澳联储改革方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/australian-treasurer-offers-opposition-rba-deal-to-pass-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财政部长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，他已向自由国家党反对派提出对储备银行改革的让步，以确保其对立法改革的支持并结束长达数月的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/australian-treasurer-offers-opposition-rba-deal-to-pass-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:33:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴将升级香港上市以吸引中国投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/alibaba-to-convert-hong-kong-listing-to-primary-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司股东已批准于 8 月 28 日将其香港上市地位升级为主要上市地位的计划，此举预计将吸引来自中国内地数十亿美元的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/alibaba-to-convert-hong-kong-listing-to-primary-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受需求担忧和加沙谈判影响，油价周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求前景严峻、产品价格下跌以及美国为确保加沙停火所做的努力，油价在周中触及 1 月以来的最低收盘价，随后开始下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 23:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
