    <item>
      <title>日元因鹰派言论上涨，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行行长上田和夫暗示仍在加息后，日元上涨。亚洲股市跟随华尔街下跌，交易员等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周五晚些时候在杰克逊霍尔发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾新光同意与竞争对手台新合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/taiwan-s-shin-kong-financial-agrees-to-merge-with-rival-taishin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾新光金融控股股份有限公司同意与一家规模较小的竞争对手合并，此举引发了新光与另一家竞争对手中国信托金融控股股份有限公司的收购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/taiwan-s-shin-kong-financial-agrees-to-merge-with-rival-taishin</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 13:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
